The NBA free-agent frenzy is here. NBA free agency 2022 officially begins at 6 p.m., when teams can legally begin speaking with free agents. Legally being the operative word, as there’s been momentum building for days toward a union between Jalen Brunson and the Knicks. Can the Knicks get it done? What will be the fallout from Kevin Durant’s bombshell trade request? Follow along as the action unfolds.